咁點解個時唔講？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"用下腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"發現連登仔真係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee479f649930f8c6aecd153a48e4af4891e72a0","tid":2059931,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac02194c5677794f3ad3e6ad534c2424b2011a33","tid":2059931,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218dfe80877bd83f1a3a0b1c17e114e736ec4eef","tid":2059931,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6146ef055205536c523c626508eb190b4792cc9f","tid":2059931,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"foreword 有講到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"但連登仔好多盲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會屌做咩份報告無bno平權件事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"點解無講bno?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"有講<br />\n<strong>Status of British Nationals (Overseas)</strong><br />\nThe events of the six months of the reporting period generated increased interest in<br />\nthe status of British Nationals (Overseas). On 4 September, a group of British<br />\nparliamentarians called for the UK and Commonwealth countries to offer Hong Kong<br />\npeople the right of abode as an &ldquo;insurance policy&rdquo;.<br />\nOn 9 September, British NGO Hong Kong Watch hosted an event in the UK Parliament,<br />\ncalling for the UK Government to consider extending the rights of BN(O) passport<br />\nholders. On 10 September, over 100 parliamentarians signed a letter to the Foreign<br />\nSecretary, calling on the UK government to urge Commonwealth countries to grant<br />\nHong Kong people second citizenship.<br />\nOn 15 September, several hundred protesters rallied outside the British ConsulateGeneral, urging the UK Government to &ldquo;review the status of &lsquo;One Country, Two<br />\nSystems&rsquo; and act against the material breach of the Sino-British Joint Declaration&rdquo;."},{"pid":"2dbd30bddd3e3c39eefc68df3309a8c6defbd57a","tid":2059931,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bee479f649930f8c6aecd153a48e4af4891e72a0","tid":2059931,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac02194c5677794f3ad3e6ad534c2424b2011a33","tid":2059931,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218dfe80877bd83f1a3a0b1c17e114e736ec4eef","tid":2059931,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"但連登仔好多盲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會屌做咩份報告無bno平權件事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"點解無講bno?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"有講<br />\n<strong>Status of British Nationals (Overseas)</strong><br />\nThe events of the six months of the reporting period generated increased interest in<br />\nthe status of British Nationals (Overseas). On 4 September, a group of British<br />\nparliamentarians called for the UK and Commonwealth countries to offer Hong Kong<br />\npeople the right of abode as an &ldquo;insurance policy&rdquo;.<br />\nOn 9 September, British NGO Hong Kong Watch hosted an event in the UK Parliament,<br />\ncalling for the UK Government to consider extending the rights of BN(O) passport<br />\nholders. On 10 September, over 100 parliamentarians signed a letter to the Foreign<br />\nSecretary, calling on the UK government to urge Commonwealth countries to grant<br />\nHong Kong people second citizenship.<br />\nOn 15 September, several hundred protesters rallied outside the British ConsulateGeneral, urging the UK Government to &ldquo;review the status of &lsquo;One Country, Two<br />\nSystems&rsquo; and act against the material breach of the Sino-British Joint Declaration&rdquo;."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"其實我扮假膠姐，唔洗咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e772d269942accd55d948416fc4d8dfc0cc37ed","tid":2059931,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfcb967514bc2c82dec037080a62a9522313227","tid":2059931,"uid":277934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"Twitter條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dd55a1dfb67fbefaab10d3f702bff397430373","tid":2059931,"uid":67963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031f63bf7682ff44dc93da1b3cf3f704a1f66daa","tid":2059931,"uid":53844,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"注意：本報告內容只包括舊年7到12月既事<br />\n<br />\n唔好問點解無講BNO平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"Foreword (Page 4) 有講架<br />\n<br />\nThere is still time for China to re-consider, to step back from the brink and respect Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy and respect its own international obligations. As I announced to Parliament on 2 June, if China enacts this legislation we will amend the arrangements for those with British National Overseas status in Hong Kong. If China follows through with its proposed legislation, we will put in place new arrangements to allow BN(O)s to come to the UK without the current 6 month limit,enabling them to live and apply to study and work for extendable periods of 12 months, providing a path to British citizenship."},{"pid":"f55be42af6d739cdf16fa48b134e8072ae756983","tid":2059931,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27dd55a1dfb67fbefaab10d3f702bff397430373","tid":2059931,"uid":67963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031f63bf7682ff44dc93da1b3cf3f704a1f66daa","tid":2059931,"uid":53844,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"注意：本報告內容只包括舊年7到12月既事<br />\n<br />\n唔好問點解無講BNO平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"Foreword (Page 4) 有講架<br />\n<br />\nThere is still time for China to re-consider, to step back from the brink and respect Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy and respect its own international obligations. As I announced to Parliament on 2 June, if China enacts this legislation we will amend the arrangements for those with British National Overseas status in Hong Kong. If China follows through with its proposed legislation, we will put in place new arrangements to allow BN(O)s to come to the UK without the current 6 month limit,enabling them to live and apply to study and work for extendable periods of 12 months, providing a path to British citizenship."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"Sorry 睇漏左"}]}